##Civil partnership in Hungary

You can get the equivalent of a civil partnership in Hungary. They are known as ‘bejegyzett élettársi kapcsolat’ or ‘registered partnerships’.

Contact a [register office in Hungary](https://kormanyablak.hu/hu/kormanyablakok) to find out about local laws and what documents you’ll need.

^[Get legal advice](/government/collections/list-of-lawyers) and check the [travel advice for Hungary](/foreign-travel-advice/hungary) before making any plans.
